				<h1 class="txt-f4 txt-s7 balance-text">Archipelago angst: How Indonesia and the US differ on air routes over sea lanes</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="article-author pv-md col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
															<a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/aristyo-rizka-darmawan">
							Aristyo Rizka Darmawan
						</a>
												</div>
							<div class="article-summary col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10">
					<p class="txt-s5 txt-f1 balance-text txt-lmd">
						UNCLOS ambiguity, again.
					</p>
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="article-main-image">
			<img class="article-main-image-img" src="https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/interpreter_article_image/public/2023-08/GettyImages-1133597482.jpg?itok=Qat1iWSI" alt="The left island is Bintan Island and the right island is Tanjung Sauh Island (Taro Hama/Getty Images)">
