    <li>
      <a class="txt-dn" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://www.lowyinstitute.org/the-interpreter/archipelago-angst-how-indonesia-us-differ-air-routes-over-sea-lanes&amp;title=Archipelago+angst%3A+How+Indonesia+and+the+US+differ+on+air+routes+over+sea+lanes&amp;summary=Archipelago+angst%3A+How+Indonesia+and+the+US+differ+on+air+routes+over+sea+lanes&amp;source=" onclick="javascript:window.open(this.href,
