    <a class="article-thumb-wrap" href="/the-interpreter/power-legitimacy-go-hand-hand">
      <div class="article-thumb"
           style="background-image: url('https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/4935283295_089de13713_k.jpg?itok=RRChWywa'">
       </div>
    </a>

    <div class="article-title">
      <h3>
        <a href="/the-interpreter/power-legitimacy-go-hand-hand">
          Power and legitimacy go hand in hand
        </a>
      </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="pv-sm">
      <div class="article-precede">
        Whatever America’s flaws and crimes – and there are many – it is a free and open democracy. China is not.
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>
													

<div class="col-sm-4">
  <article id="node-" class="article-card article-card-default" data-history-node-id="36472" about="/the-interpreter/archipelago-angst-how-indonesia-us-differ-air-routes-over-sea-lanes" class="node-type-interpreter-debate">
